Package: polyglot-ai
Version: 0.2.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, libgl1, libxcb-xinerama0, libxkbcommon0, libxcb-cursor0
Maintainer: Polyglot AI Contributors
Description: AI-powered coding assistant desktop app
 Polyglot AI is a desktop coding assistant for Linux that supports
 multiple AI providers including OpenAI, Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini,
 and xAI Grok, with a full IDE-like interface including a code editor,
 file explorer, chat panel, review tools, and terminal.
